People in this comment section should notice two very important points. There are two groups of posters: there are ACTUAL members either a) making encouraging statements or, b) voicing legitimate criticism and then there are NON-member posts that typically fall into three categories: a) people who are being rude or voicing their excitement over the chaos, b) people who pretend that the rude comments are coming from members and c) people who are posting here 24/7 fake white knighting and pretending that the valid criticism coming from the members is a sign of entitlement.
